TITLE: Using makeRef() in Custom Components for Multiple References
DESCRIPTION: Using makeRef() in a custom component to return multiple references, allowing access to different parts of a composite component for animation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/redotvideo/docs/blob/main/src/content/motion-canvas/references.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_10

