TITLE: Serving Revideo Project using CLI - Bash
DESCRIPTION: This Bash command uses npx to invoke the 'revideo serve' CLI which starts a local development server, building and serving all required assets. The local server enables testing and immediate feedback by exposing your player at http://localhost:4000/player. Run this inside your Revideo project directory for development or preview purposes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/redotvideo/docs/blob/main/docs-old/docs/api-reference/player-react/player.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npx revideo serve
```
